# 📈 Real-Time Market Dashboard

A full-stack real-time trading dashboard built with **Node.js, Express, WebSocket, React, TypeScript, and Recharts**.

The application simulates a stock/crypto market environment with:

- REST APIs for tickers and historical data
- WebSocket-based real-time price updates
- Interactive chart visualization
- Clean modular architecture

---

## 🚀 Project Overview

This project simulates a simplified trading dashboard where users can:

- View a list of available tickers
- Select a ticker to see its historical price chart
- Observe live price updates via WebSocket

The backend simulates price movements in memory, while the frontend displays both historical and real-time data.

The goal was to design a clean, scalable architecture that resembles real-world trading systems.

